text:
From docs reading it's not obvious what object is returned by `redis.subscribe()` call and what attributes/methods the object has.
The most important attrs are `.get()` and `.iter()` but all public api worth to be documented.
title: Channel object is not documented

text:
The `Channel` object is [documented](http://aioredis.readthedocs.io/en/v0.2.8/api_reference.html#aioredis-channel).
However, it is not mentioned in pub/sub methods
Now the issue can be closed, isn't it?
